<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Margarethe von Hohenlohe-Brauneck, Gräfin von Schwarzburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass man nach Rückkehr des Jakob Topler, Bürger zu Nürnberg, dessen Antwort übersendet.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_17" id="8r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l1">Frawn Margrethen von Braunecke </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l2">weylunt Grefin cʒu <expan>Swarcʒpurg<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_17_r1l4">Edle vnd liebe fraw . / Als Jr vns geſchrıben habt von / Jacoben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l5">Toplers vnſers Burgers vvegen . / der iſt cʒu der cʒeit nicht anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l8">Aber wenn er herheim kumpt . So vvöllen wir Jn darümb <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> cʒu rede </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l9">ſecʒen / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">daran weẏſen ſo wir peſtt mügen / </del> ewr gnade dann <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_line_1576231468259_230">ein antvvurtt wiſʒen laſʒ . / wer die / von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> deʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen vordert </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l13">wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden lieb vnd dinſt beweiſen möchten / deʒ weren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_r1l14">wir willig vnd teten daʒ allcʒeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> . / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>vj̃</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Exaltat<ex>ionis</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_17_line_1576231509837_250"><expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> <expan>Cruc<ex>is</ex></expan> / Anno ıx<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_17" id="8r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Margrethen von Braunecke, weylunt grefin czu
                                <expan>Swarczpurg<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edle und liebe fraw, als ir uns geschriben habt von Jacoben Toplers, unsers
                        burgers, wegen, der ist czu der czeit nicht anheim. Aber wenn er herheim
                        kumpt, so wöllen wir in darümb <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> czu rede seczen
                        und ewr gnade dann <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein antwurtt wiszen lasz,
                        wer die von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dez <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen vordert;
                        wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden lieb und dinst beweisen möchten,
                        dez weren wir willig und teten daz allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>vi</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>exaltat<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan>
<expan>cruc<ex>is</ex></expan> anno ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
